@page
@addTagHelper *,Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.TagHelpers
@model HarryPotter.Pages.IndexModel

@{
    Layout = "_Layout";
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/StyleSheet.css" />
}

<body style="background-color:black; color:ghostwhite;">

<div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4">
        Hogwarts School of <br />
        Witchcraft and Wizardry
    </h1>
    <img src="https://i.imgur.com/GNtAFrh.jpeg" />
</div>
<br />
<p>Contgratulations on your acceptance into Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry! Our fine institution of magic welcomes you! In order to have everything ready to go when you arrive, please allow the Sorting Hat below to assign you to a house. Then feel free to learn more about that house or any other below. </p>

<p>We are excited to teach you to become a powerful witch or wizard! You can get a sneak peek at some of the spells, charms, jinxes and more by accessing our Spells section below. But please remember the Hogwarts rule: you may not perform any spells while in the Muggle world!</p>

<p>See you on the Hogwarts Express departing from platform 9 3/4 in a few weeks!</p>

<p>Congratulations on your acceptance into Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry! Our fine institution of magic welcomes you! In order to have everything ready to go when you arrive, please allow the Sorting Hat below to assign you to a house. Then feel free to learn more about that house or any other below. </p>

<br />
<br />
<br />
<div>
    <section>
        <div class="text-center">
            <h2>Sorting Hat</h2>
            <br />
            <img src="https://i.imgur.com/o0HDcDc.png" width="150" />
            <br />
            <br />
        </div>
        <div>
            <p>Welcome to Hogwarts! All students are sorted into one of four Houses upon arrival at Hogwarts. </p>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>


<div>
    <form method="get" asp-page="Index2">
        <!-- Button trigger modal -->
        <button class="btn btn-light" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#basicExampleModal">
            Sort me into a House
        </button>

     </form>

 
 
</div>

<br />
<br />
<br />
<section>
    <div>
        <h3>Learn More About Each House at Hogwarts</h3>
        <form method="post" asp-page="/Results/HouseInfo">
            <label for="house">Select a House: </label>
            <select name="house" id="house">

                <option value="Gryffindor">Gryffindor</option>
                <option value="Hufflepuff">Hufflepuff</option>
                <option value="Ravenclaw">Ravenclaw</option>
                <option value="Slytherin">Slytherin</option>
            </select>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-light">Submit</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</section>
<br />
<br />
<br />

<section>
    <div>
        <h3>Spells</h3>
        <p>There are many powerful spells you will learn during your education at Hogwarts. Click below to see a list of what you may learn.</p>

        <form method="post" asp-page="/Results/SpellsResults">
            <div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-light">Hogwarts Spells</button>

            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</section>

<br/>
<br/>

</body>
